{
  "stem": "4570.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I was doing all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on top of it, I had this marvelous job, eventually, in a German bank-- which was a-- a first real Nazi Bank-- as a telephonist, and make photocopies of all their documents.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I filled out a form, obviously, they only ask what religion I have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't say, is your father a Jew?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I held the job for over one year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell me, do you remember your father having to wear a star?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, everybody had to wear a star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean when-- when-- when-- when my boyfriend and I went out, I had to either put one on or he had to have a briefcase that he held.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, a-- a lot of Jews did that, you know-- have the star when they needed to have it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they didn't need it, they had a briefcase, and they were hiding it behind it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was already very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't mind putting it on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March '39, that was obviously when-- when the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't so scary, because we just-- we just had no idea what will eventually happen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that my parents were very distressed when the Germans marched in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because I hadn't met my boyfriend in March-- I met him in June-- it-- I mean, sure, I knew it something bad happening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But look.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When You're 16 years old, those things, they-- they-- they don't seem as real as they really are.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I saw is-- I think it was they came very early in a-- in the morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was sort of still dark.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
